                <head>218. Summary of Conclusions of Presidential Review Committee Meeting<note
                        n="1" type="source" xml:id="d218fn1">Source: <persName corresp="#p_CJE_1"
                            >Carter</persName> Library, National Security Affairs, Staff Material,
                        International Economics File, Box 32, <persName corresp="#p_PR_2">Rutherford
                            Poats</persName> File, Summit: Tokyo. Confidential. The meeting was held
